Main technologies used:
  1. Programming language: Javascript ES6 to ES8
  2. Frontend framework: Vue JS 
  3. Backend framework: Node / Express JS
  4. NoSQL Database: MongoDB 

Requirements:
  1. Node.js. Link: https://nodejs.org/en/download/ 
  2. MongoDB. Link: https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/community

  * If watson-developer-cloud package manager requires python - Link: https://www.python.org/downloads/

How to run :
  1. Open Command Prompt.
  2. Go to client directory folder(cd client) using cmd and type npm install. // "npm install" is only required if running the program for the first time. 
  3. Then to the main directory(cd ..) type npm install.
  4. To the main directory type "npm run dev" - runs both the client and the server.

  * Url path to admin dashboard - http://localhost:8080/admin-dashboard

  IBM Watsons API Reference: https://console.bluemix.net/apidocs/assistant


